I have tried just doing div.innerHTML = infowindowContent(f); with the content wrapped in backticks and an "<a>" tag which works but I cannot seem to use a custom component or tag (carousel) inside it.

What am I doing wrong? Can divs be clickable when created with ReactDOMServer.renderToString? Or is it some other issue?

